---
/**
 * SECCIÓN: Grilla Bento de Servicios
 * PROPÓSITO: Desglosar los 4 servicios técnicos principales con un diseño visualmente jerárquico.
 * CONTENIDO:
 *  - Mantenimiento Preventivo (Gran formato con imagen y lista de tareas).
 *  - Afilado de Tijeras (Enfoque en técnica artesanal).
 *  - Calibración de Máquinas (Precisión micrométrica).
 *  - Repuestos Certificados (Garantía y disponibilidad).
 * INTERACCIÓN:
 *  - Efectos hover en tarjetas (sombras y bordes).
 *  - Transición de color en imágenes de escala de grises a color al pasar el cursor.
 */
---

<!-- Services Bento Grid -->
<section class="py-j-xl bg-surface-container-lowest technical-grid">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-j-margin max-w-7xl">
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-end mb-j-xl gap-j-sm">
      <div class="max-w-xl">
        <h2 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-on-background uppercase mb-j-xs">Nuestros Servicios</h2>
        <div class="h-1 w-20 bg-primary"></div>
      </div>
      <p class="text-on-surface-variant font-body-md max-w-xs">Soluciones especializadas para equipos BaByliss PRO y
        herramientas de alta gama.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-j-gutter">
      <!-- Maintenance -->
      <div
        class="md:col-span-8 group relative overflow-hidden bg-white border border-outline-variant hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row h-full">
          <div class="p-j-lg md:w-1/2 flex flex-col justify-between">
            <div>
              <span class="text-label-md font-label-md text-primary uppercase mb-j-xs block">PREVENTIVO</span>
              <h3 class="font-headline-sm text-headline-sm mb-j-sm">Mantenimiento Preventivo</h3>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-on-surface-variant">
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span
                    class="material-symbols-outlined text-[18px]">check_circle</span> Limpieza profunda ultrasónica
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span
                    class="material-symbols-outlined text-[18px]">check_circle</span> Lubricación de ejes
                  cinemáticos</li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span
                    class="material-symbols-outlined text-[18px]">check_circle</span> Revisión de circuitos
                  eléctricos</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <button
              class="mt-j-lg border border-on-background text-on-background px-6 py-2 text-label-md font-label-md uppercase hover:bg-on-background hover:text-white transition-all self-start">Consultar
              Tarifa</button>
          </div>
          <div class="md:w-1/2 relative h-64 md:h-auto">
            <img
              class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-500"
              data-alt="Professional technician's hands wearing black nitrile gloves carefully cleaning a high-end chrome hair clipper with specialized tools in a bright, minimalist workshop. The background is pristine and white with organized technical equipment. The lighting is soft and focused on the metallic reflections of the equipment, conveying a sense of premium service and expert precision."
              src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida/ADBb0uikYsnyoozMzJ79Oyeub7SPgUftOgUYCGIxgdhD8WRw4Olt_wYTSHbQZiQKdKgZO2ds-VNzRLO0wMzHjevztZaapwfTnMrfO3yxThdC5u1AUsKWfmpRAdaxssXMCqhTjxJbhxwxAi8pjWu3n4U_qrrMyvSil-p2bqZARfjnqAKavRf0sTcxaj1Grbfx73e9sQBR3klkr-UlUpvKPouKgmFPQ8bRl5D7nOCy6Tmumsi4VnAqwg_k83iIJxZz5p_L7BKRCwAXXFw_ffU" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- Sharpening -->
      <div
        class="md:col-span-4 bg-white border border-outline-variant p-j-lg flex flex-col justify-between group hover:border-primary transition-all">
        <div>
          <span class="text-label-md font-label-md text-primary uppercase mb-j-xs block">ARTESANAL</span>
          <h3 class="font-headline-sm text-headline-sm mb-j-sm">Afilado de Tijeras</h3>
          <p class="text-on-surface-variant mb-j-md">Restauramos el ángulo de corte original mediante técnicas
            tradicionales y piedras de alta granulometría.</p>
          <img class="w-full aspect-square object-cover mb-j-md grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0 transition-all"
            data-alt="Extreme close-up of a professional barber scissor blade being sharpened. Tiny metallic sparks are visible as the steel meets the sharpening surface. The aesthetic is industrial and high-precision, with a focus on the sharp edge and the texture of the high-quality steel. The background is a clean, neutral silver and grey, maintaining the minimalist technical style of the brand."
            src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida/ADBb0ugbVMbxh5w8mszc086MJB9XjWVPfzqpyTkG4fmYCch7xwS4qhJukTyyVt7FexQgBkKQW4COpur2WzvxClLsjn5B07cVFTEG98RXRuQE4QhXDkaodimj0aaWPLJ25dBWXDd9NRWaDF-YPE5HcH5cv27vsx6IkP0QYukg9d1ro3cyxamjExTTsafWs5ZgiKPURdnoyjF3596zQWeEOFmxE9RxZd-86EnFZjmyaPpLyqkp53_J3wYwpzJiBsF0Y7lMzAG-AgnQEmiZkh8" />
        </div>
        <a class="flex items-center gap-2 text-label-md font-label-md uppercase border-b border-transparent hover:border-primary w-fit transition-all"
          href="#">Ver Galería de Afilado <span class="material-symbols-outlined">arrow_forward</span></a>
      </div>
      <!-- Calibration -->
      <div
        class="md:col-span-4 bg-surface-container-low border border-outline-variant p-j-lg flex flex-col justify-between group">
        <div class="mb-j-lg">
          <span class="text-label-md font-label-md text-primary uppercase mb-j-xs block">PRECISIÓN</span>
          <h3 class="font-headline-sm text-headline-sm mb-j-sm">Calibración de Máquinas</h3>
          <p class="text-on-surface-variant">Ajuste micrométrico de cuchillas para cortes 'Zero Gap' sin irritación.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="relative overflow-hidden h-48 border border-outline-variant">
          <img class="w-full h-full object-cover"
            data-alt="A technical blueprint overlaying a photograph of a barber machine motor and blade assembly. Technical measurements and red Sienna-colored focus points highlight the adjustment areas. The image is clean, brightly lit, and highly informative, emphasizing the scientific and calibrated approach to machine repair and performance optimization."
            src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida/ADBb0ug26pimlYuVWW2uo-YQjPrhV5BqDljrMXNK7Zrv08gVvLuFGiHmbuyzw1VpnVs-M9l1j8rbHLOeMMC6thsFSmOWTzAVfwq_2qg5Dn87qIRhMGTFw8XUA6h47fyiYPvjlP5-WgTtTgO0MkzaQBe2S3Ex62B7niad1eOkffxMwbb85SnQfG3pmxo3WY5S3W4YqaNwKDHYqdzFk4kW_vf8sXMy8LX4rZHctnket40zUP2RAnACU5oP3UNIRC0eRydTXeWg1yJmYNbta10" />
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- Spare Parts -->
      <div class="md:col-span-8 bg-white border border-outline-variant p-j-lg group relative">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-j-lg items-center">
          <div class="md:w-1/3">
            <img class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0 transition-all"
              data-alt="An organized display of genuine replacement parts for high-end hair machines, including motors, blades, and circuit boards. Each part is placed on a clean white surface with systematic spacing. The lighting is even and bright, highlighting the quality and authenticity of the components. The overall aesthetic is one of technical reliability and industrial excellence."
              src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida/ADBb0ugy0lj4JoSo6_x9VihrFwUvYXf7aMWFT-Zute6824KHu_kt8OxfpdTkZSRdln3efNMiR27b3VpBWYTd0VVU0iH2wpdnHpho9r4EJExs1Mpx4D-YWwfkVpn3AJ9aLogM52rRoXx20P3ZPNw33ygTibV46kvgJb44PTBUo0-QHXRcolC_xESn7bJA61lQ7_pVVU5yKhm9jlhwFU1utCMnI-C2uoVPZZX1dNu7A2V3GpWk7Uc4GHOMf7W8VjpANmYTT9w0-juanUdBpkw" />
          </div>
          <div class="md:w-2/3">
            <span class="text-label-md font-label-md text-primary uppercase mb-j-xs block">ORIGINALES</span>
            <h3 class="font-headline-sm text-headline-sm mb-j-sm">Repuestos Certificados</h3>
            <p class="text-on-surface-variant mb-j-md">Contamos con un inventario exclusivo de motores, baterías y
              carcasas originales BaByliss PRO. Garantía de fábrica en cada cambio.</p>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-j-sm">
              <div class="border-l-2 border-primary-container pl-j-sm">
                <p class="text-label-md font-label-md uppercase">Disponibilidad</p>
                <p class="font-headline-sm">98%</p>
              </div>
              <div class="border-l-2 border-primary-container pl-j-sm">
                <p class="text-label-md font-label-md uppercase">Garantía</p>
                <p class="font-headline-sm">6 Meses</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
